Hi, I'm Androklis a Web Developer

Who Is Androklis?

A curious Full-Stack Developer.

I'm passionate about building things and seeing them come to life. For me, User Experience, clean code, and a clear purpose are paramount.

I hold a BSc in Engineering Informatics from International Hellenic University, and a certificate in application development from COMCAVE.COLLEGE Stuttgart. Additionally, I have certifications from Udemy, including 'The Complete Web Developer Course,' 'Angular,' and 'ASP.NET Core REST API Real World Application.'

I'm actively seeking new projects and am available for freelance work. Please feel free to reach out!
